When I started the research on
this about 2 and 1/2 years ago,

00:43:22.810 --> 00:43:25.999
no bank had expressed any
real interest in this.

00:43:25.999 --> 00:43:28.040
And even big consulting
firms, when I asked them,

00:43:28.040 --> 00:43:30.000
like what are your big
bank clients saying,

00:43:30.000 --> 00:43:31.875
they're like, well, it's
