00:49:04.180 --> 00:49:08.920
to margin that's applied on that
through added-value services?

00:49:08.920 --> 00:49:11.070
Like you mentioned
the cash payment

00:49:11.070 --> 00:49:14.930
of 2% margin or the 0.25%.

00:49:14.930 --> 00:49:18.810
So what's the impact
if that is clear to us

00:49:18.810 --> 00:49:23.550
the whole chain of
the transaction?

00:49:23.550 --> 00:49:26.960
ALEX TAPSCOTT: So
the systems are

00:49:26.960 --> 00:49:30.450
transparent in that you can
see that money is moving

00:49:30.450 --> 00:49:32.210
and that value is moving.

00:49:32.210 --> 00:49:35.170
